values: HA I know all of you guys are jealous! Yea that's right...I am watching Full House! Yea so K-mart didn't work out....ugh! I want to work at the pet store at the mall....Those animals are soooo cute I love them! Today was an interesting day...some of the happenings were somewhat upsetting but, I got over them! That's all I've got......

I am so bored....still have homework I've gotta do. My mom says I'm grounded....but I'm not so ya know! Ummmm today was a good day. I've been having a lot of good days lately, how cool is that?!?! Anywho I guess I'm about to go, I've got an application to fill out! (For K-mart yea that's right K-mart it's cool.....really!) Im out!

I finally decided to get a LiveJournal...hmmm I don't get Katie...she's not talkin to me the same as before. Ever since me and Joey started going out she's been like blah when she's talkin to me. I'm so confused by her right now. Well she just left me and Joey is at work. No one else is online and I don't feel like calling anyone. So I guess it's time I should really start working on my homework. I've put it off long enough. I'm gonna play some HIM and get to working....yea right I'll probably be right back. At least I'm gonna try.
